6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Blackbox AI and JetBrains AI share a solid foundation of core features including Autocomplete, Code Generation, Multi Language, Ide Integration. On the other hand, JetBrains AI uniquely offers Debugging and Refactoring and Test Generation and Documentation, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Blackbox AI holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while JetBrains AI scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Blackbox AI offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $0, compared to JetBrains AI's starting price of $10/mo. Blackbox AI has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. JetBrains AI does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
